{"tid":906412,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[FG勿進］如何接受人工到達職位頂薪","createTime":"2018-11-18T03:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T15:43:19.000Z","uid":194298,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"08d80a16d427540a7df153b05c8bfb43fa71a203","tid":906412,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"私人工唔同政府工有point可照，但大概每間公司甚至每一行業都會對係果個職位既人有個價值共識<br />\n<br />\n假如係同一位置做左一段長時間，自知已經接近甚至到達該位頂薪<br />\n<br />\n但又未有能力條件升到下一level，各位會點面對<br />\n每年只得1-3%基本通漲升幅甚或有時係零添<br />\n<br />\n見到出面FG都話同自己差唔多人工（2x k)，好氣餒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9695ea1418a44f32ba97ec2bc01173c2eb862419","tid":906412,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"諗下點先有得升，轉工？進修？carry d 大project?"},{"pid":"cf143696036dedd476a9221b112eaba38c14b85f","tid":906412,"uid":985,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"一般而言，都係英文能力限制左個高度。"},{"pid":"434245a2ca154d4cba2bbd2ef79bcf82eeb8902d","tid":906412,"uid":19979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"私人工一係靠識人<br />\n一係靠轉工"},{"pid":"d434c7708d774b4469abf540fde648cef2fe649f","tid":906412,"uid":64009,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"轉工多50%是常識吧"},{"pid":"7ac9a71c8002c78dc98cb2e481c39ea78f3c438b","tid":906412,"uid":84702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"24790f458c96ff53dafc4a9b0f04845879fdbdf2","tid":906412,"uid":89066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"轉工？ 進修再上？ ptbf/ptgf?"},{"pid":"19de3a2453438cdc21c885034465ca8645352079","tid":906412,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"我上司有同我講過<br />\n要轉工唔係問題<br />\n幾時走都得<br />\n但係一定要確保下份工最少要高過依家人工30%"},{"pid":"77e43164fe03c